Commodity:
Phosphoric esters and their salts, including lactophosphates; 
their halogenated, sulphonated, nitrated or nitrosated 
derivatives.

Artificial graphite; colloidal or semicolloidal graphite; 
preparations based on graphite or other carbon in the form of 
pastes, blocks, plates or other semimanufactures.

Human hair, dressed, thinned, bleached or otherwise worked; 
wool or other animal hair or other textile materials, prepared for 
use in making wigs or the like.
